"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n難得人地吹風BNO平權<br />\n推推post吓勁多淡友入場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支狗第2日聽到即刻衝出嚟吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />借個位嚟push吓<br />\n<br />\n英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n// The UK should give Hong Kong citizens full UK nationality as a means of reassurance amid the current standoff with Beijing, the chair of the influential Commons foreign affairs committee has argued. (The Guardian)//<br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ1 : 簽咗咁多聯署 / 英國佬唔會幫我地 /英國佬都唔想收咁多新移民喇 / 英國佬講咗咁耐都冇做過嘢 簽嚟都冇用<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗1分鐘搞掂又冇成本嘅嘢點解唔做咗先 <br />\n<br />\n六合彩咁難中你又買<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n今次係有下議會議員帶頭講要俾full citizenship BNO holder<br />\n10萬人都簽唔到叫人地點幫你啊<br />\n我地要送子彈啊<br />\n<br />\nQ2: 好多97後都冇BNO 我地唔可以扔低佢地<br />\n<br />\nA: 有BC又有幾多人會即刻走 <br />\n反而有咗後路可以更盡情咁去抗爭<br />\n同埋到時大量英國國民喺香港 （ ff住先）可以增加英國嘅談判籌碼<br />\n真係去到最壞情況都可以諗方法帶埋d細路走<br />\n<br />\nQ3: 佢要tick Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign<br />\n我 得 / 冇BNO簽唔簽得？<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗verify citizenship 自己諗簽唔簽<br />\n只要提供 email address + 英文名 ＋選Location + Postal code<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅take返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打000000 或 N/A<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsotKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=92dbb536\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自己一個簽係唔夠 請share出去<br />\n例如：<br />\nLib Dem<br />\nJo Swinson<br />\n各大香港英國報章<br />\nTwitter<br />\n英國MPs"},{"pid":"d1f89c6aef86e06246d1850472882c569c197c8e","tid":1486064,"uid":137204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:52:09.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"ab42dd67d1a7f8afea2525bc0b0968b726d23d13","tid":1486064,"uid":132572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85144c8d6ddf265657b1575877f19bef687c8cf3","tid":1486064,"uid":267806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:05:31.000Z","msg":"攬炒係唯一出路"},{"pid":"9c2345a20c4585675e9ca227b533fedababa93dc","tid":1486064,"uid":181035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:24:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3789eb55c4f005c12eac4f7c4cfba28ca61df327","tid":1486064,"uid":126730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:25:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5533826ca2e707a0f00adb4bbd2d9d46c5a9a0cb","tid":1486064,"uid":132572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:36:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0e3567e442f8ab46c14f13f9161a22acba07f8","tid":1486064,"uid":162541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:45:58.000Z","msg":"推，少左好多行動post"},{"pid":"ed12ddc6379a103115ec9352affeda3808415b90","tid":1486064,"uid":132572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac0e3567e442f8ab46c14f13f9161a22acba07f8","tid":1486064,"uid":162541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:45:58.000Z","msg":"推，少左好多行動post"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T12:39:22.000Z","msg":"真係少左<br />\n真係無得攰..<br />\n一攰就乘虛而入"},{"pid":"ea573a9bf691ed42024fdaba3dd2470bae654cf0","tid":1486064,"uid":162541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T12:45: